properties.doc: Unique identifier for the test profile run, must contain only lower-case alphabetic, numeric, underscore or hyphen characters.

properties.name: targetResourceConfigurations
properties.doc: Configurations of the target resource on which the test profile ran.

properties.name: status
properties.doc: The test profile run status.

properties.name: errorDetails

properties.name: startDateTime
properties.doc: The test profile run start DateTime(RFC 3339 literal format).

properties.name: endDateTime
properties.doc: The test profile run end DateTime(RFC 3339 literal format).

properties.name: durationInSeconds
properties.doc: Test profile run duration in seconds.

properties.name: testRunDetails
properties.doc:
Details of the test runs ran as part of the test profile run.
Key is the testRunId of the corresponding testRun.
